Package: spca
Type: Package
Title: Sparse Principal Component Analysis
Version: 0.6.0
Date: 2014-12-14
Author: Giovanni Maria Merola
Maintainer: Giovanni Merola <lsspca@gmail.com>
Description: Computes Least Squares Sparse Principal Components either by a
    Branch-and-Bound search or with an iterative Backward Elimination
    algorithm. Sparse solutions can be plotted, printed and compared using the
    methods included.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    formatR,
    knitr,
    ggplot2,
    reshape2
Imports:
    MASS
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
